400 = n/2 (50)
Number of terms, n = 16
As we know, the last term of AP series can be written as;
Last term, l = a + (n − 1) d
45 = 5 + (16 − 1) d
40 = 15d
Therefore,
Common difference, d = 40/15 = 8/3
