Sn = n/2 [2a + (n – 1)d]
7/2 [2a + (7 – 1)d] = 700
[2a+(6)(-20)]/2 = 100
a + 3(−20) = 100
a − 60 = 100
a = 160
Therefore, the value of each of the prizes was Rs 160, Rs 140, Rs 120, Rs 100, Rs 80, Rs 60, and Rs 40.
